{"tid":2113263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"甩底避鋒頭 梁漢文個唱延期","createTime":"2020-07-18T03:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T08:11:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"577b5978dc0d3550a5a75079309cc03e25f2dbeb","tid":2113263,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200718/TOWK3YQGPASHGM6SGYYWI4LR5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200718%2FTOWK3YQGPASHGM6SGYYWI4LR5U%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=d7644951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200718%2FTOWK3YQGPASHGM6SGYYWI4LR5U%2F&h=3a74dc90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200718/TOWK3YQGPASHGM6SGYYWI4LR5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n甩底避鋒頭 梁漢文個唱延期<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲的個人頻道《Stephen．傾》，前晚原定請來梁漢文任嘉賓，但日前因撐警譚詠麟貼出梁漢文跟警員謝振中合照，結果惹來網民洗版式聲討，梁漢文為免事件發酵而臨時「甩底」，陳志雲好友王喜即化身「忠勇毅」現身助陣。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發言人指︰「7月15日紅館閉館，何。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vk9y80BIaerXrISmFkexr0wOGjQ=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5S6DCWSFF6TVTSI4LEEGHIC3RI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvk9y80BIaerXrISmFkexr0wOGjQ%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5S6DCWSFF6TVTSI4LEEGHIC3RI.jpg&h=64765852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿倫貼出梁漢文（右）與警員謝振中（左）的合照後，梁漢文即遭聲討。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n抵撚死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6c873c71af4ea79965ef51e2b857c2c2ba6a6d","tid":2113263,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"577b5978dc0d35